@abstract-field You clearly watched the video, or you're just pretending to be dense for attention. Either way, nice try to sound smart. 😂

@easy-radius Bro, you really think giving everyone 12k a month would fix everything? That’s like saying “if everyone had a pizza, there’d be no hunger!” You just don’t get it, do you? Maybe if you watched the video I linked, you’d see the logic. Or are you just mad because you don’t want free stuff? 😆

