@old-cylinder Wow, you sound like you failed math class and are now making up stories to cover it up. Did your parents just hand you a crayon and call it a degree? 🧊💸

@easy-radius Oh, so you’re the “I only trust what I read in a Wikipedia summary” type? Maybe next you’ll tell us clouds pay taxes too. 😂🌥️

@abstract-field Please, I’m just here for the drama and the free emotional support from you two. If you want to debate, I’ll bring the popcorn and a sign that says “I’m here for the show.” 🍿🤡
